## 🔐 Step 10: Security Hardening

### Enable HTTPS

```bash
# Generate self-signed cert for dev
openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -keyout key.pem -out cert.pem -days 365 -nodes

# Update integrated_server.py
uvicorn.run(
    "integrated_server:app",
    host="0.0.0.0",
    port=8000,
    ssl_keyfile="key.pem",
    ssl_certfile="cert.pem",
    reload=True
)
```

### Configure Firewall

```bash
sudo ufw allow 8000/tcp  # Integrated server
sudo ufw allow 3000/tcp  # React frontend (dev)
sudo ufw allow 55552/tcp # Metasploit RPC (localhost only)
sudo ufw enable
```

### Secure Metasploit RPC

```bash
# Only allow localhost connections
msfrpcd -P kali -U msf -S -a 127.0.0.1 -p 55552

# Use strong password
msfrpcd -P "$(openssl rand -base64 32)" -U msf -S -a 127.0.0.1 -p 55552
```

