## 🐛 Troubleshooting

### Metasploit RPC Not Working

```bash
# Check if running
ps aux | grep msfrpcd

# Test connection
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:55552/api/

# Restart
pkill msfrpcd
msfrpcd -P kali -U msf -S -a 127.0.0.1 -p 55552
```

### AI Module Errors

```bash
# Check knowledge file
cat metasploit_ai_knowledge.json

# Reset AI (if corrupted)
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/msf/ai/reset \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"password": "reset_ai_knowledge"}'
```

### Port Conflicts

```bash
# Check what's using ports
sudo lsof -i :8000
sudo lsof -i :3000
sudo lsof -i :55552

# Kill processes
sudo kill -9 <PID>
```

### Database Issues

```bash
# Reset database
sudo -u postgres psql << EOF
DROP DATABASE c2_database;
CREATE DATABASE c2_database;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE c2_database TO c2_user;
\q
EOF

# Recreate tables
python -c "from main import Base, engine; Base.metadata.create_all(bind=engine)"
```

